## Conventions

- **Images:** All project images live in `/static/projects/images/`. Naming format: `[project-slug]-[descriptor].[ext]` (e.g. `ot-reservations-before-after.gif`). Reference in content as `/projects/images/filename.ext`
- **Export:** PNG at 2x resolution from design tools; GIF for animations
- **Drafts:** Set `draft: true` until ready to publish
- **Ordering:** Use `params.weight` (lower = higher priority)

